==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Contradistinction
<hw>Con`tra*dis*tinc"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>Distinction by contrast.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>That there are such things as sins of infirmity in
<qex>contradistinction</qex> to those of presumption is not to be
questioned.</q> <rj><qau>South.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Contradistinctive</ent>⟦br⟧
